not stay."
</P>
<P>
Complete contrasting opinions on the game split them and made
it impossible to work together, Blatter said.
</P>
<P>
Johansson had earlier said he would like to see that he became
the next FIFA president while Blatter stayed as the secretary
general to assist him. 
