</P>
<P>
Gao, from Northeast China Liaoning province, garnered 60 points
to level the world record with 113 hits in the 29-shooter event.
</P>
<P>
Zhu Mei from the Southeast Hunan province took the silver with
101 hits and 59 points, while Ma Huike from the Central Henan
province finished the third with 100 hits and 58 points. 
</P>
</TEXT>
