<HEADLINE> New Ocean Shipping-Railway Coordinated Transport Line Opens </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SHANGHAI, May 28 (Xinhua) -- China Shipping Group Container
Shipping Co. Ltd. announced today that it will open a new ocean
shipping-railway coordinated transport line with railway transport
departments based in northeast China.
</P>
<P>
The Shenyang Railway Administration, the Harbin Railway
Administration and Yingkou Port Administration will provide the
new service together with the firm.
</P>
<P>
