secretary Thursday.
</P>
<P>
Mahathir is scheduled to deliver a keynote address on
"Revitalization of the Japanese and East Asian Economies" in Tokyo
on June 2 at the fifth symposium of the Institute for
International Monetary Affairs, which is an affiliate of the
International Monetary Fund (IMF).
</P>
