at deepening understanding between Japan and other Asian nations.
</P>
<P>
The financial and economic crisis affecting the region as well
as the worrying state of the Japanese economy is expected to top
the agenda of both the IMF symposium and the Nikkei conference.
</P>
<P>
The regional economic crisis which broke out last July
following the attack on the Thai baht had a contagion effect on
other currencies and economies, especially that of Thailand,
Indonesia, the Philippines and Malaysia.
</P>
<P>
Mahathir is scheduled to return on June 5. 
