organization and the Congress, Estrada had won a landslide victory
in the presidential election. He garnered about 10.7 million votes
cast, some 6.4 million votes ahead of his nearest rival de
Venecia.
</P>
<P>
Philippine Congress is expected to announce on Friday the final
official results of the presidential and vice presidential
elections. 
