<HEADLINE> Shanghai Stock Index Down </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, May 28 (Xinhua) -- The Composite Stock Index on the
Shanghai Stock Exchange finished at 1,397.89 today, down 1.64
points from the previous session, according to the Guangfa
Securities Co. Ltd.
</P>
<P>
The SSR-30 index, based on 30 blue chips that are selected from
more than 200 A shares for domestic investors on the Shanghai
