<HEADLINE> Beijing Logs Price Information on Internet </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, May 28 (Xinhua) -- Beijing's Municipal Bureau for
Price Management has logged local price information on the
Internet.
</P>
<P>
The program is expected to provide a basis for government
policy makers and to better serve society.
</P>
<P>
Most of the information placed on the Internet is free of
charge.
