<P>
BEIJING, May 28 (Xinhua) -- Chi Haotian, vice-chairman of the
Central Military Commission and minister of National Defense, met
this morning with a delegation from the DPRK People's Army
led by the vice-director of its General Political Bureau, Ji
Yongchun.
</P>
