<HEADLINE> Romania to Keep Strong Ties with Hungary </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BUCHAREST, May 27 (Xinhua) -- Romanian Foreign Minister Andrei
Plesu said Wednesday the good relationship between Romania and
Hungary will continue to grow, no matter what changes occur in the
Hungarian government.
