<HEADLINE> Netherlands Draw 0-0 With Cameroon in Friendly </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BRUSSELS, May 27 (Xinhua) -- The Netherlands proved their
superiority to Cameroon but failed to make it on the mark as they
were held to a goalless draw on Wednesday in a soccer friendly
match in Arnhem, the Netherlands.
</P>
<P>
With the high-flying Clarence Seedorf of Real Madrid on the
right wing and Marc Overmars of Arsenal on the left, the Dutch
never lacked of scoring chances, but could not find the net.
</P>
