Bergkamp, on the bench.
</P>
<P>
He seemed to be decided to leave the Arsenal striker, who is
still suffering a hamstring injury, for the World Cup finals.
</P>
<P>
Rigobert Song marshalled a competent Cameroon defence and
goalkeeper Jacques Songo'o made dozens of diving saves to stop the
Dutch attacks.
</P>
<P>
The Dutch will play Paraguay on Monday and Nigeria on June 5,
while Cameroon have only one warm-up match remaining, against
Denmark on June 5. 
