<HEADLINE> Chinese Nuclear Power Plant Using Domestic Parts </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
CHENGDU, May 28 (Xinhua) -- The first Chinese boron injector,
a key part of 1-million-kw nuclear power plants, got approval from
the contractor here on Monday.
</P>
