projects over the next two years, according to Wen Bingyou,
Dongfang's general manager.
</P>
<P>
Gan Daoming, a senior official in charge of the nuclear power
industry in Sichuan Province, said that the province is placing
greater importance on manufacturing nuclear power equipment and
taking advantages of its industries, with Dongfang in the lead.
