Beijing at the age of 93. Shu, regarded as the master calligrapher
who inherited the unique Chinese tradition of calligraphy, was
honorary president of the Chinese Calligraphers' Association.
</P>
<P>
 "Xinhua Daily Telegraph"
</P>
<P>
