new oilfield in the Pearl River Estuary Basin in the eastern part
of the South China Sea, the China Offshore Oil Nan Hai East
Corp. reports.
</P>
<P>
The Panyu 4-2 Oilfield is 160 km to the southeast of Hong Kong,
in 90 m. of water. It has estimated reserves of 20 million tons.
</P>
